{"tid":2229283,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"還柙手足越嚟越多，可以點？","createTime":"2020-10-04T09:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T19:04:02.000Z","uid":8435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce85e680a7589cac589e2e796165f76293255aa5","tid":2229283,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:13:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101341284739985/posts/208429530697826/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101341284739985%2Fposts%2F208429530697826%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=d3de3d03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101341284739985/posts/208429530697826/</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;資助盒2.0&gt;﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n好不幸地，面對住越嚟越多嘅清算，手足計劃嘅錢用得越嚟越快，又再一次要大家幫手。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n⚠️想幫手既有心人們麻煩留意圖三既注意事項⚠️﻿<br />\n<br />\n(另外可能麻煩大家記低個order number方便我地核數)<br />\n﻿<br />\n恕我哋再長氣講一句，懇請大家唔好用贖罪嘅心態嚟買資助盒，只有堅持直到勝利先係對手足最好嘅禮物。各位香港人，各司其職盡力做好本份，不鬥黃，不分化。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n最後，好想再一次多謝 邵家臻邵家臻議辦、Joshua Li 李俊晞李俊晞議辦、DC Sean Mock office, Chessa 彩虹邨服務聯會 - 莫灝哲議員辦事處莫灝哲議辦、彭卓棋 Michael Pang彭卓棋議辦 、隨心物流 Whatever Logistics Limited隨心物流 同幾位幫我哋搵物資嘅手足，無佢哋就無手足計劃。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n如果對我哋嘅手足計劃或者物資盒有咩疑問，歡迎大家搵我哋，我哋會盡力協助同解答。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n歡迎大家share 依個post出去🙇🏻&zwj;♀️﻿<br />\n<br />\n資助盒link: <a href=\"https://jimmyjungle.online/collections/csd-items/products/%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%97%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E7%9B%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjimmyjungle.online%2Fcollections%2Fcsd-items%2Fproducts%2F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%259B%2592&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=44614672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jimmyjungle.online/collections/csd-items/products/%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%97%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E7%9B%92</a><br />\n﻿<br />\n#手足計劃﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿<br />\n#零食 #日用品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DxF9mkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDxF9mkC.jpg&h=3c1851e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PjxS3y0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPjxS3y0.jpg&h=df0a90da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyQA1kJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyQA1kJ.jpg&h=61884248&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69475b058325b8bbe479c8a06bf91c83574fbae1","tid":2229283,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"有需要嘅可以聯絡Jimmy Jungle申請資助盒<br />\n<br />\n想食零食變肥豬都可以去佢哋度買零食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0eee4f9af54aff27a8fb5def544722d81251eb","tid":2229283,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd59b89b318a9d490b01499b2529b806eeb88ce6","tid":2229283,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有做筆友"},{"pid":"fa79a2628ecab2bdb649196da37575ee1beecf08","tid":2229283,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"我冇錢但可以義教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最簡單既野冇人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe497cd5cd0e281ff134e0afe51881a2cf35d94","tid":2229283,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd59b89b318a9d490b01499b2529b806eeb88ce6","tid":2229283,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有做筆友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"